Run Android reftests and crashtests with font size inflation.

THE PATCHES reference-match-text-runs AND add-text-size-adjust ARE
SUFFICIENT TO GET REFTEST GREEN WITH THIS PATCH.

HOWEVER, CRASHTEST-1 STILL CRASHES (WITHOUT DIAGNOSTIC) IF ALL OF
layout/base, layout/forms, AND layout/generic ARE RUN TOGETHER BUT NOT
IF ANY ONE DIRECTORY IS RUN ALONE.

